title: [Vornavis, West Road]
description: The path slopes up a ridge to the northeast, but flattens out to wide, featureless plains to the west.  The ridge borders a large lake to the southeast.  Flocks of nocturnal birds fly up and away from the lake, crossing the ridge into the plains to the northwest.
